.The properties of the galaxy counterpart of this DLA are consistent with the prediction that metal-rich DLAs are associated with the most luminous of the DLA-galaxy counterparts. {\textcopyright} 2010 The Authors. Journal compilation {\textcopyright} 2010 RAS.},
